{"tid":1180450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子縉庭山寓所燒炭　阿哥發現惜為時已晚","createTime":"2019-05-31T23:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T06:54:13.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"727289ad4392585569bf98bb2eb365e5d19cd3e3","tid":1180450,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:55:35.000Z","msg":"昨日(31日)晚上10時許，一名40歲姓盧男子，在荃灣國瑞路168號縉庭山一單位燒炭自殺，事主兄長揭發，大驚報警求助。警方接報到場，發現盧倒臥浴室，旁邊有一盤燒過的炭，救護員將昏迷事主送院，其後證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警員現場未有檢獲遺書，經初步調查，相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open嗡」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=93c1d408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190601/mobile/bkn-20190601015425557-0601_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190601%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190601015425557-0601_00822_001.html&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=f1a8d3d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190601/mobile/bkn-20190601015425557-0601_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f6aaef00360c437299ecf58bbda59787c9cdb164","tid":1180450,"uid":73604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"RIP...."},{"pid":"e978cfb7391d7d3a0fa560673b911581288a6793","tid":1180450,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"解脫"},{"pid":"0e446d9b33d8fface68a563411b9aa66e06da2fa","tid":1180450,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid